TITLE: Kalki Avatar | Kaliyug Ke Ravan Aur Sadhu Ka Vesh | Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta | #kaalbhairav
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mD4ELo-rEfo
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Deepak Kaushik exposes a self-proclaimed "Yogi Lalit Kumar" from Rajasthan who sent extremely threatening and abusive voice messages to Noor Ananta Ji. The video plays multiple audio clips where this individual threatens to strip her clothes in public, create doctored viral images to defame her, calls her a "vaishya" (prostitute), threatens to come to her home in Ludhiana, and boasts about having stripped many Naga sadhus and Goris at the Kashi ghats. He claims to be a Kaal Bhairav devotee and a lawyer, using these credentials to intimidate.

Deepak frames this as evidence of the Kaliyug's Ravans hiding in sadhu's garb -- drawing a direct parallel to how Ravan kidnapped Sita by disguising himself as a sannyasi. He argues that if this person can speak this way to someone of Noor Ananta Ji's spiritual stature (whom he describes as the 12th Rudra Avatar, "Baarve Rudra" -- HanuKaalBhairav), imagine what he does to ordinary women and devotees who come to him. He calls this systematic blackmail of vulnerable people.

He challenges the Naga and Aghori communities to respond to such fake babas who claim to have stripped their own kind. He urges women and common people to free themselves from such fraudulent spiritual predators, and announces that the Noor Ananta energy has already identified and sorted the genuine from the fraudulent in the sadhu community -- as predicted at the beginning of Kumbh, when Noor Ananta Ji said the saint community would split into two factions.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Fake sadhu "Yogi Lalit Kumar" exposed for sending threatening, sexually abusive messages to Noor Ananta Ji -- evidence of Kaliyug's Ravans in spiritual disguise
- The child in Noor Ananta Ji's arms is described as "Baarve Rudra" (12th Rudra Avatar) -- HanuKaalBhairav incarnation, not to be disrespected
- The prediction made at Kumbh's start is coming true: the sadhu/saint community is splitting into genuine seekers and fraudulent predators
- Such blackmailing fake babas are a systemic problem in the spiritual marketplace -- the energies are now actively exposing and sorting them
- Noor Ananta Ji's energy has empowered "Nagas in suit-boot" (awakened warriors in ordinary clothes) in every household, ready to respond

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: The unmasking of Kaliyug's Ravans in sadhu disguise -- the divine energies are now intolerant of any disrespect toward the avatar and are systematically exposing fraudulent spiritual predators as part of the cleansing required for Yug Parivartan.

